{"tid":2343742,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"從安七炫、東方神起、SJ、太妍到 Red Velvet 和 aespa⋯⋯SM 免費線上演唱會元旦登場！","createTime":"2020-12-28T07:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T03:37:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad4964cbf51be56ce0f26d9fd236a1daa342fc9","tid":2343742,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"SM 旗人藝人近期接連舉行線上演唱會或見面會，接下來橫跨好幾代的多組歌手也將大舉登場，在 2021 年第一天免費送上精彩表演！<br />\n<br />\nSM Entertainment 今天宣布將於 2021 年 1 月 1 日下午 1 點（韓國時間）舉行線上演唱會《SMTOWN LIVE &quot;Culture Humanity&rdquo;》，同時公開了預告海報及演出陣容。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3c7cdb196d82094b94011fa09b752e90/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-28/132619-890765.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3c7cdb196d82094b94011fa09b752e90%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-28%2F132619-890765.jpg&h=e32fb25f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n包括安七炫 (Kangta)、東方神起、Super Junior、少女時代隊長太妍、SHINee 泰民、EXO 伯賢和 KAI、Red Velvet、NCT 系列團體 NCT U、NCT 127、NCT Dream 與 WayV、SuperM 乃至最新出道的小師妹 aespa 都會登場，還有三位 DJ Raiden、GINJO 和 IMLAY，陣容可說十分華麗。<br />\n<br />\n過去多年來，SM Entertainment 早已在世界各地舉行過家族演唱會《SMTOWN LIVE》，這次則難得地直接在線上舉行。1 月 1 日透過 NAVER V LIVE、YouTube、推特、Facebook、TikTok、KNTV（日本）都能免費收看，大家別忘了準時鎖定囉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：SM Entertainment)"},{"pid":"ebf693c52e4edfce86ad007f3113e34785c37af2","tid":2343742,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"足球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa72b272af77a8df16fb4e5b47ce6c860990d2c7","tid":2343742,"uid":313222,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:21:14.000Z","msg":"irene<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33df124294d2247d9022955940a9e88155e42659","tid":2343742,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebf693c52e4edfce86ad007f3113e34785c37af2","